      "description": "Used car in fair overall condition. It starts, runs, and drives, but it shows noticeable wear inside and out consistent with age and regular use. Expect cosmetic blemishes, a worn interior, and some age-related issues or maintenance needs, but it should still be a usable vehicle for a buyer looking for basic transportation at a reasonable price. Not a perfect car, but an honest fair-condition driver.",
