    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for someone seeking dependable transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows clear signs of age and use, but it remains an appealing choice for a handy buyer, commuter, or anyone looking for an affordable everyday option. A straightforward value with room to make it your own.",
