      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride, a solid project, or a handy parts car? This one has definitely seen some life, but it still has plenty to offer for the right buyer. Great candidate for someone who enjoys tinkering, needs inexpensive transportation, or wants a vehicle they can work on without breaking the bank. Priced to move and being sold with honesty\u2014what you see is a straightforward opportunity.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong project or budget driver with solid mechanical bones and plenty of upside for the right buyer. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels composed enough to be a worthwhile platform for restoration, weekend wrenching, or inexpensive transportation. It shows age and will need cosmetic and reconditioning work, but for someone who knows their way around maintenance and repairs, this is an affordable entry point with real potential. Priced to move and well suited to an enthusiast looking for a fixer with usable fundamentals.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car. Not pretty, but priced to move. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of presence that makes you look back after you park it\u2014a seasoned driver with real personality and plenty of story left to tell. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone who wants affordable wheels with character, a hands-on project, or a practical runabout that doesn\u2019t pretend to be precious. There\u2019s a rugged charm here: honest, unpolished, and full of potential for the next owner who sees value in a car with soul. If you appreciate the beauty of a machine that\u2019s lived a little and still stands ready for its next chapter, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "An affordable, no-nonsense vehicle that offers practical transportation at a very accessible price. This car shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values budget-friendly ownership and understands it is being offered as-is, but it still presents a solid opportunity for basic daily use, a backup vehicle, or a project. If you\u2019re looking for inexpensive entry into car ownership from a trusted seller, this is a compelling value.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car you can put to work right away or tinker with over time? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. A great fit for someone who wants inexpensive transportation, a project, or a practical runaround without spending a fortune. Priced to reflect its condition and ready for someone to give it a good home.",
      "price": 4800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Tough, honest driver with strong project potential. The powertrain pulls well, the transmission engages as it should, and it has the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes it a great candidate for someone who wants an affordable car to sort and enjoy. Not a cosmetic showpiece, but the chassis feels solid and it offers a usable platform with good parts value and plenty of life left for the right owner. If you want an inexpensive entry point into a dependable daily, weekend project, or donor with worthwhile running gear, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
